latestIgtvVideos.title: HAPPY PRIDE EVERYONE!
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
So proud to be QUEER and so proud to be part of @beccacosmetics creative team with my wife @yvonnetheartist over the last 3 years. 

Working with this brand and the amazing humans that make it all happen has been the ultimate experience 💕

Here she is the last Hooray... "Hi, Angel": it’s Becca’s last ever Shimmering Skin Perfector! Created to celebrate individuality, It’s  a beautiful, iridescent shade designed for all skin tones. 
 
In support of the LGBTQIA+ community and the brands continued commitment to mental wellness, BECCA Cosmetics is honored to donate $50,000 to our partners @trevorproject 

Exclusively available on beccacosmetics.com

#queer #beccacosmetics #trevorproject #supportqueeryouth #supportqueerartists #queerartists #queermentalhealth #weexist #highlightyourpride

latestIgtvVideos.title: Cuttin Creases with @thecreativemakeup
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
GUESS WHAT... @yvonnetheartist and I are teaching our first IN PERSON class with @themakeupshow called “MAKE UP IS ART”

Such a dream to work for @danessa_myricks and get to create industry shifting campaigns like this. For me this is why I am a creative director, to create space and give voices to people who deserve to be seen. 

Thank you Danessa for being a loving and incredibly smart leader and for hiring me + trusting my vision 💕 @partwolfla  thank you for being the best partner, interviewer, advocate and marketer 💕 @miguelitolittle thank your being an incredible photographer and beauty master, ideas are nothing without you there to bring them all to life. 

My incredible team who I could do nothing within out! @makeupbyviv___  @iamolga @gkarpinmua @bri.swing @katpackis @linhhair @fernandordz.studio Audrey, Misha and Josiah! And that’s just creative, It takes a whole damn village 💕 we shot 5 days of content for this shoot between assets, campaign, social & product + endless hours editing, retouching and designing. 

And all the wonderful talent  @nicklujan_artistry @sterlingtullnyc @sarahhhhhart @beautyxgenn @iyannathemodel @soy_mr.maria + any of the other wonderful humans I didn’t tag, thank you for sharing your story and your beautiful faces with the world. 

Happy Pride 🏳️‍⚧️ 🖤 🏳️‍🌈
